name: Sex, Drugs, why not?
description:
David might be an angel, and death unavoidable, but these earthly pleasures are just a necessity.

Also, what else can you do when Facebook's down?

2000x2000 px PNG file

This is the 3rd installment of the Todxs Caretas / Original Fakes series, that consists of collectible avatars depicting myths, symbols, monsters and icons from everyday culture, high arts and pop culture.

All of them made by hand on papercut technic
